<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Operator Onboarding | redBus</title>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Grow your business with the world's #1 bus platform</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Get started with redBus now</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-metrics">
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-value">5 Crore+</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Total Passengers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-value">7 Cr+</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Unique Customers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <span class="metric-value">8000+</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Operators Connected</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-cards">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon card-icon-bus">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="48" height="48" rx="8" fill="#e9ecef"/><path d="M12 28h24v4H12v-4zm2-10h6v6h-6v-6zm8 0h6v6h-6v-6zm-10 2l2-6h20l2 6H12z" fill="#1a73e8"/><circle cx="36" cy="20" r="6" fill="#22c55e"/><path d="M34 20l3 3 4-5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Register your bus with redBus</h3>
          <p>Start selling on the world's largest bus ticketing platform today</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Register Now</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon card-icon-learn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="48" height="48" rx="8" fill="#e9ecef"/><circle cx="24" cy="20" r="8" fill="#1a73e8"/><path d="M24 14v4l2 2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M18 32c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.7 6 6v2H18v-2z" fill="#1a73e8"/><circle cx="34" cy="18" r="5" fill="#22c55e"/><path d="M32 18l2 2 3-3" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Learn about bus business</h3>
          <p>Unlock 30%+ ROI with a high-growth Intercity bus opportunity</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Know More</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon card-icon-agent">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="48" height="48" rx="8" fill="#e9ecef"/><circle cx="24" cy="16" r="6" fill="#1a73e8"/><path d="M14 38v-2c0-4 4-7 10-7s10 3 10 7v2H14z" fill="#1a73e8"/><rect x="26" y="26" width="12" height="10" rx="2" fill="#1a73e8" opacity="0.9"/><path d="M28 28v6h2v-3l2 1 1-2-3-2h-2z" fill="#fff"/><circle cx="34" cy="22" r="4" fill="#22c55e"/><path d="M32 22l1.5 1.5 2.5-2.5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Register as travel agent</h3>
          <p>Grow your business by booking tickets for your clients and earn commissions effortlessly</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Go to seatseller</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section platforms">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="platforms-card">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Go live across platforms</h2>
          <p>Maximize your reach with your inventory live on most of the major platforms</p>
        </div>
        <div class="platforms-logos">
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/makemytrip.svg" alt="Make My Trip" />
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/goibibo.svg" alt="Goibibo" />
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/irctc.svg" alt="IRCTC" />
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/amazonpay.svg" alt="Amazon Pay" />
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/gpay.svg" alt="G Pay" />
          <img class="platform-logo" src="/images/logos/seatseller.svg" alt="Seat Seller" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section capabilities">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cap-header">
        <h2>redBus capabilities powering India's online bus business</h2>
        <p>Powerful tools that will help your business reach milestones</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap-layout">
        <div class="cap-left">
          <div class="cap-item cap-item-active">
            <img src="/images/logos/revmax-logo.png" alt="revMax" class="cap-logo" />
            <p class="cap-tagline">Automate pricing and maximise revenue</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-item">
            <img src="/images/logos/redpro-logo.png" alt="redPro" class="cap-logo" />
            <p class="cap-tagline">Manage, promote, and grow your bus business</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-item">
            <img src="/images/logos/nova-logo.png" alt="nova" class="cap-logo" />
            <p class="cap-tagline">Buy best quality bus parts at better prices</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&#9658;</div>
        <div class="cap-right">
          <div class="cap-screenshot-wrap">
            <img src="/images/revmax-dashboard.png" alt="revMax dashboard" class="cap-screenshot" />
          </div>
          <div class="cap-caption">
            <strong class="cap-caption-title">revMax</strong>
            <p>revMax is a dynamic pricing tool that automatically sets seat fares using real-time demand and market trends to maximize operator revenue</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section why-now">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <h2>Why now is the <span class="highlight">time to start</span> bus business?</h2>
          <p>Your chance to profit from India's growing travel market</p>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Get Started</button>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cards">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-illus">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 248 169" width="248" height="169" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="248" height="169" rx="8" fill="#f0f4ff"/><rect x="72" y="30" width="68" height="109" rx="10" fill="#fff" stroke="#dde3f5" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="78" y="42" width="56" height="8" rx="3" fill="#e8edfc"/><rect x="78" y="56" width="56" height="8" rx="3" fill="#e8edfc"/><rect x="78" y="70" width="56" height="8" rx="3" fill="#e8edfc"/><rect x="78" y="84" width="40" height="8" rx="3" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.7"/><circle cx="108" cy="109" r="14" fill="#22c55e"/><path d="M103 109l4 4 8-8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><rect x="14" y="50" width="50" height="30" rx="6" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.15"/><text x="39" y="70" font-family="Arial" font-size="16" font-weight="800" fill="#1d4ed8" text-anchor="middle">30%+</text><circle cx="30" cy="100" r="12" fill="#7c3aed" opacity="0.15"/><text x="30" y="104" font-family="Arial" font-size="9" fill="#7c3aed" text-anchor="middle">₹</text><rect x="180" y="60" width="55" height="22" rx="6" fill="#fef3c7"/><text x="207" y="75" font-family="Arial" font-size="11" fill="#d97706" text-anchor="middle">Weekly</text></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-body">
            <h3>30%+ annual returns with weekly payments</h3>
            <p class="benefit-desc">Get weekly payments with high profits in the growing bus market</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-illus">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 248 169" width="248" height="169" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="248" height="169" rx="8" fill="#eff6ff"/><rect x="20" y="70" width="140" height="52" rx="10" fill="#1d4ed8"/><circle cx="45" cy="96" r="10" fill="#93c5fd"/><circle cx="145" cy="96" r="10" fill="#93c5fd"/><rect x="55" y="86" width="80" height="20" rx="4" fill="#2563eb"/><circle cx="124" cy="35" r="22" fill="#7c3aed" opacity="0.9"/><text x="124" y="41" font-family="Arial" font-size="14" font-weight="800" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">50L+</text><circle cx="55" cy="136" r="16" fill="#1d4ed8"/><rect x="65" y="128" width="30" height="16" rx="3" fill="#e85d04"/><circle cx="160" cy="138" r="14" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.8"/><path d="M153 138l4 4 8-8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/><text x="210" y="80" font-family="Arial" font-size="11" fill="#1d4ed8" text-anchor="middle">18%↑</text></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-body">
            <h3>50L+ Travelers &amp; growing every day in market</h3>
            <p class="benefit-desc">The bus market is growing fast at 18% giving you more bookings</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-illus">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 248 169" width="248" height="169" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="248" height="169" rx="8" fill="#f5f3ff"/><rect x="60" y="30" width="130" height="90" rx="8" fill="#e5e7eb"/><rect x="66" y="36" width="118" height="78" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d1d5db"/><circle cx="90" cy="72" r="16" fill="#7c3aed" opacity="0.8"/><rect x="112" y="60" width="60" height="8" rx="3" fill="#e8edfc"/><rect x="112" y="74" width="40" height="8" rx="3" fill="#e8edfc"/><path d="M125 120h-8v8" stroke="#d1d5db" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><rect x="104" y="120" width="40" height="6" rx="3" fill="#7c3aed"/><circle cx="200" cy="50" r="18" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.2"/><path d="M192 45l4 12 8-16" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="30" cy="60" r="14" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.15"/><path d="M24 56l6 8 8-12" stroke="#1d4ed8" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-body">
            <h3>Online operations makes it zero hassle</h3>
            <p class="benefit-desc">Operate easily with getting permits, bookings, &amp; payments</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-illus">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 248 169" width="248" height="169" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="248" height="169" rx="8" fill="#f0fdf4"/><path d="M20 100 Q60 40 120 70 Q180 100 230 60" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="6 3"/><path d="M20 130 Q80 90 140 110 Q200 130 230 100" fill="none" stroke="#1d4ed8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/><circle cx="20" cy="100" r="6" fill="#d84a4a"/><text x="20" y="92" font-family="Arial" font-size="9" fill="#d84a4a" text-anchor="middle">A</text><circle cx="120" cy="70" r="6" fill="#d84a4a"/><text x="120" y="62" font-family="Arial" font-size="9" fill="#d84a4a" text-anchor="middle">B</text><circle cx="230" cy="60" r="6" fill="#1d4ed8"/><text x="230" y="52" font-family="Arial" font-size="9" fill="#1d4ed8" text-anchor="middle">C</text><rect x="14" y="20" width="70" height="28" rx="6" fill="#1d4ed8" opacity="0.9"/><text x="49" y="38" font-family="Arial" font-size="13" font-weight="800" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">1000+</text><rect x="166" y="106" width="70" height="48" rx="8" fill="#fff" stroke="#e6e6e6"/><text x="201" y="127" font-family="Arial" font-size="9" fill="#666" text-anchor="middle">New Routes</text><text x="201" y="143" font-family="Arial" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#16a34a" text-anchor="middle">Untapped</text></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-body">
            <h3>1000+ Untapped routes gives big opportunity</h3>
            <p class="benefit-desc">Find profitable new routes with smart pricing &amp; operational tools</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>See what our operators are saying about us</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <blockquote>Partnering with redBus helped us scale our operations and reach more customers across India.</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Rajesh Bafna</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Co-owned entrepreneur from Dada Brothers</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <blockquote>redBus platform is easy to use and the support team is always there when we need them.</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Jaspreet Singh Hahar</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Founder of King Luxuries</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <blockquote>We have seen significant growth in our bookings since we joined redBus. Highly recommend.</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Mr. Pradeesh Karthi</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Delta Transport PVT Ltd (Tamil Nadu)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section register-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Be part of world's largest bus booking platform</h2>
        <p>Register with your phone number to get started instantly</p>
      </div>
      <div class="register-form-wrap">
        <form action="#" method="post" id="register-form">
          <div class="phone-input-group">
            <select name="countryCode" aria-label="Country code">
              <option value="+91">+91</option>
            </select>
            <input type="tel" name="mobile" placeholder="Add your mobile number" aria-label="Mobile number" required />
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Generate OTP</button>
          </div>
          <label class="captcha-row">
            <input type="checkbox" name="captcha" required aria-label="I'm not a robot" />
            I'm not a robot
          </label>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <p>Find answers to common questions about partnering with redBus</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">What are the benefits of being a redBus partner?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">You get access to India's largest bus ticketing audience, dynamic pricing tools, and weekly settlements. redBus also helps you list on multiple platforms like MakeMyTrip, Goibibo, and more.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">What is the process of bus registration on redBus?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Register with your phone number, verify with OTP, submit your bus and route details, complete documentation, and go live. Our team will guide you at every step.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">Is there a partnership fee?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">redBus does not charge any upfront partnership fee. You pay a commission on successful bookings. Contact us for detailed commercial terms.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">How can I manage my Inventory on redBus?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">You can manage schedules, fares, and seat inventory through the redBus operator dashboard (redPro). Updates reflect in real time across all partner platforms.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">How do I get paid as a redBus partner?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Settlements are done weekly. You receive payouts directly to your registered bank account after deduction of commission and any adjustments.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">How can I know if a seat is booked?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">The operator dashboard shows all bookings in real time. You can also enable notifications to get alerts for new bookings.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">&copy; redBus Operator Onboarding</div>
</footer>

<script src="/dist/js/main.bundle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
